<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 4 (Veigue) - Start</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ティトレイ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Tytree</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ヴェイグ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Veigue</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ゼロス</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Zelos</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>やめろ、ヴェイグ！
何考えてやがんだ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Stop, Veigue! What the heck are you thinking?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>13</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>おそらくオレの氷は
自然やマナに程近い力なんだろう。
だからマナ枯渇の影響を受けて暴走した</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>My ice is most likely close in relation to
nature and Mana, right? That's why it went
berserk as an effect of the Mana drying up.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>12</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>だが、力の本質が近いなら
オレの力を世界樹に
注ぎ込んでやる事も可能なはずだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But if the essence of our powers are
close in relation to them, then it should
be possible, in that case, for me to pour
my power right into the World Tree itself.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>12</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>無駄なことはやめときな。
たかが人間一人分の生命力じゃ
世界樹は蘇らねぇよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Stop doing reckless stuff.
The life force of just one man isn't 
gonna be enough to revive the World Tree.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>少しだけでいいんだ。
村の氷を溶かせるだけの力さえ
取り戻してくれれば……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Just a small amount is fine. If I can get just enough
of its power to melt the ice affecting the village...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>12</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そんな事のために
お前は全生命力を使い果たすのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And you're just gonna up and use all
your life force on something like that?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>よせよ、ヴェイグ！
どういう事かわかってんのか！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Knock it off, Veigue!
Do you even get what that would mean?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>13</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>死んじまうんだぞ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're gonna die, you know?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>13</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……わかってる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...I know.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>12</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>わかってねぇよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You sure DON'T get it!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>13</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……すまない。　オレは行く</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...I'm sorry. I'm going.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>12</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>行かせねぇぞ、ヴェイグ。
ぶん殴ってでも、止めてやる！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I won't let ya go, Veigue.
Even if I gotta punch ya, ya ain't goin'!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>13</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
